================================================================================
    Create a root account
================================================================================

Launch shell, and run the following command:

$ sudo passwd root

After this, system will ask you enter password of current user; 
After enter current user's password, system will ask you set new password
for root account, and then re-type this password.

Then, you will see info tells you that the 
new password for root account is set successfully.

================================================================================
    Login as root account
================================================================================

$ su root

Then, enter root password

================================================================================
    END
================================================================================
